text: Osredek () is a small settlement north of Rob in the Municipality of Velike Lašče in central Slovenia. The area is part of the traditional region of Lower Carniola and is now included in the Central Slovenia Statistical Region.Velike Lašče municipal site ==References== ==External links== *Osredek on Geopedia * Category:Populated places in the Municipality of Velike Lašče
title: Osredek, Velike Lašče
